longBusinessSummary: D Mecatronics Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in the engineering, design, manufacture, sale, and installation of tube related automated systems used by automotive parts and assembly suppliers worldwide. The company offers components, integrated systems, and robotic modules. Its tube related automated systems include seat frame systems, IP tube systems, and integrated bend weld systems. The company was formerly known as Equity Retirement Savings Distributors, Inc. and changed its name to D Mecatronics Inc. in March 2005. D Mecatronics Inc. was founded in 2002 and is based in Mississauga, Canada.
